{"id":162220,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011617/","date":"2011-06-18T06:00:18Z","modified":"2011-06-18T06:00:18Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/6/17","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2011/jun/17/ai-weiwei-tate-display\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">泰特现代艺术馆用新展览向艾未未致意</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“虽然艾未未没有讲话的自由，但他的作品可以让人们听到他的声音”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>MSNBC – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/06/17/6880115-for-chinas-crooked-officials-america-is-the-place-to-be\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对于中国的贪官而言，美国是首选之地</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“在中国，当官的风险很低”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/06/17/china-s-brewing-political-storm/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国正在酝酿中的政治风暴</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“对于独立候选人来说，手续上的障碍只不过是丑陋的非法阻挠的代名词”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">麦克拉齐</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2011/06/16/115944/claims-of-injustice-spur-wave.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国，社会不公激起动荡</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“打人对他们来说太平常了，随便一点原因他们就会动手”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>CNN – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/06/17/china.riot.town.yoon/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的骚乱之城</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“即使边上就有警察盯着，他们也毫不害怕地对着外国记者大倒苦水”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-16/china-s-inflating-political-bubble-business-class.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">小心中国的政治泡沫</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“其专制制度在面临即将出现的经济减速时，会难于应付社会稳定问题”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/06/17/never-fear-taiwan-congress-is-here/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾别害怕，美国的国会会帮你</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“美国不能因为中国的压力而疏远与台湾的关系”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲哨兵</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3259&#038;Itemid=168\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">缅甸内战背后的中国之手</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国对能源的追求很可能引发了缅甸的冲突”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国家利益</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nationalinterest.org/print/commentary/the-dubious-agenda-the-sco-5478\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“上合组织”令人生疑的议事日程</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“上合成员国利用反恐名义加紧侵犯其公民的人权”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38070&#038;cHash=a9dde1807ede588ee61e51d4c395b813\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在尼泊尔的战略优势</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尼泊尔的政治僵局和毛派的崛起为中国扩大在那里的影响提供了良机</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38068&#038;cHash=295dfd670418c45d9892f8e27168c0d1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共强化对法院的控制</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“强调稳定压倒一切的原则，会导致人治而不是法制”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110617/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_south_china_sea\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在南海举行军事演习</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“演习持续三昼夜，共有</span><span>14</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艘舰艇和两架军用飞机参加”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38067&#038;cHash=a532245963039aa11786b9d1ca5d332e\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾在南海争端中处于关键位置</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最近南海的紧张局势给台湾海峡两岸的关系带来了新的动向</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/06/18/why-not-to-sweat-about-china/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么不用担心中国？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中越南海争执引起许多不安，但是中日以往类似的争执表明，冲突并非不可避免</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8581437/China-to-boost-coastal-forces-amid-sea-tensions.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国加强海监实力应对紧张局势</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“这一举动显示中国决心保卫其海权与主权”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>–<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/ap-interview-aquino-warns-china-to-stay-away-from-philippine-waters-in-territorial-spat/2011/06/17/AGzQRWYH_story.html?wprss=rss_asia-pacific\"> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社专访：阿基诺警告中国远离有争议的菲律宾水域</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“虽然我们是小国，但不会任人摆布”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/us-seeks-chinese-help-as-alarm-grows-over-violence-in-southern-sudan-ahead-of-independence/2011/06/16/AGoXVeXH_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国寻求中国帮助解决苏丹南部的暴力局势</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“我们希望北京利用这个机会重申制止暴力行为的重要性”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大赦国际</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.amnesty.org/en/news-and-updates/china-must-arrest-sudanese-president-2011-06-16\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国必须逮捕苏丹总统</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国不应允许巴希尔进入境内，如果他真的来了就要逮捕他”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-17/consumer-spending-fades-in-china-economy-after-peak-days-.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济中的消费者支出下降</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“</span><span>2006</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">到</span><span>08</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年房地产市场火热，我们可以赚到很多。现在高潮已经过去了”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110617/wl_nm/us_russia_china_gas\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中俄未能达成</span>30<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年期天然气供应协议</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“这事不能太草率，双方都需要表现出灵活性。我们还会继续谈下去”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2011/jun/17/china-vital-interests-greek-crisis\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">希腊危机对中国的关键利益带来威胁</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“欧洲国家的经济能否克服困难摆脱危机，对于我们至关重要”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《明镜》周刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.spiegel.de/international/europe/0,1518,768754,00.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人偷偷地“山寨”奥地利小镇</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“我们不高兴有人在背后干这种事情”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/06/china-see-no-fortune-hear-no-fortune.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：眼不见，心不烦</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——只禁止奢侈品广告，而不是从根本上解决问题，是典型的政治鸵鸟政策</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110617/wl_asia_afp/chinaweatherfloods\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国水灾造成逾百万人口撤离</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“洪水已造成至少</span><span>168</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人死亡，八个省逾百万人撤离”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-6089942257137368508?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":800,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}